        <div class="MCBreadcrumbsBox_0"><span class="MCBreadcrumbsPrefix">  <![CDATA[ ]]></span><span class="MCBreadcrumbsSelf">Installer help file (setup)</span><span class="MCBreadcrumbsDivider"> &gt; </span><span class="MCBreadcrumbsSelf">Standard setup</span><span class="MCBreadcrumbsDivider"> &gt; </span><span class="MCBreadcrumbsSelf">Setting up activities</span><span class="MCBreadcrumbsDivider"> &gt; </span><span class="MCBreadcrumbs">How to create supervision activities</span>
        </div>
        <h1>How to create supervision activities</h1>
        <h3>Activities with notification actions (fax, text message (SMS, e-mail, print, remote call)</h3>
        <ol style="list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#InstallareConfigurarePeriferiche">Setting up peripherals</a>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="2">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#ConfigurareCanaliNotificaDest">Setting up notification channels used by peripherals and addressees</a>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="3">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#FareTestCanaliNotifica">Testing notification channels</a>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="4">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#DefinireFasceOrarie">Setting time bands</a>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="5">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#CreareNotificheSchedulate">Creating scheduled activities</a>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="6">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#ImpostareNotificheAllarmiEventi">Setting alarm/event notifications and actions</a>
                </p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <h3>Activities with field actions</h3>
        <ol style="list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#ConfigurareAzioniRele">Setting relay actions</a>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="2">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#FareTestCanaliNotifica">Testing</a>
                </p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <hr style="color: #808080;height: 1px;float: alignleft;" color="#808080" size="0" align="center" width="100%" />
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="InstallareConfigurarePeriferiche"></a>Setting up peripherals</p>
        <ol style="list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Setting up installed peripherals
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">PlantVisorPRO Shell</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Computer management</span> set the peripherals that are installed (see chapter <a href="Sistema-installa__gestione_computer.htm">System-install: computer management</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="ConfigurareCanaliNotificaDest"></a>Setting up notification channels used by peripherals and addressees</p>
        <ol style="list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Setting up notification channels
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">I/O configuration</span>, for each channel type (fax, text message -SMS-, e-mail, Remoto) set connection modes (see chapter <a href="Config-canali__introduzione.htm">Notifications-channels: setup</a>).</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="2">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Defining typical recipients for each notification channel
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>For each physical channel (fax, text message -SMS-, e-mail, Remoto) define a list of potential contacts.</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <table style="border-left-color: #000000;border-left-width: 1px;border-right-color: #000000;border-right-width: 1px;background-color: #c0c0c0;left: 0px;top: 38px;margin-left: 40px;width: 90%;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" width="90%" bgcolor="#C0C0C0">
                        <col style="width: 6.855%;" />
                        <col style="width: 93.145%;" />
                        <tr valign="top">
                            <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 6.855%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" valign="middle" width="6.855%">
                                <p class="Note">
                                    <img src="../Resources/Images/AAtips.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />
                                </p>
                            </td>
                            <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 93.145%;padding-right: 1px;padding-left: 1px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" width="93.145%">
                                <p>Always include a channel test contact.</p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="ConfigurareAzioniRele"></a>Setting relay actions</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Setting relays to be started
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">I/O configuration</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Relay</span><span>,  </span>set the activation status for all relays and the timer for timed relays (see chapter <a href="Config-canali__configurazione_rele.htm">Notification-channels: relay setup)</a></p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="FareTestCanaliNotifica"></a>Testing notification channels</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Simulating an action request
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">I/O configuration</span>, test all set notification channels selecting test contacts (see chapter <a href="Test_periferiche__introduzione.htm">Notifications-channels: test</a>).</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <table style="width: 100%;border-left-color: #000000;border-left-width: 1px;border-right-color: #000000;border-right-width: 1px;background-color: #c0c0c0;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#C0C0C0" width="100%">
            <col style="width: 6.855%;" />
            <col style="width: 93.145%;" />
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 6.855%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" valign="middle" width="6.855%">
                    <p class="Note">
                        <img src="../Resources/Images/AAwarning.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />
                    </p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 93.145%;padding-right: 1px;padding-left: 1px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" width="93.145%">
                    <p>The communications channel used by scheduled activities must always be tested. An activity that used an channel that was not tested is indicated in the <span style="font-weight: bold;"><a href="Attivita__sinottico.htm">Dashboard</a></span> page in menu <span style="font-weight: bold;">Alarm and event management</span> or<span style="font-weight: bold;"> Scheduled activity management.</span></p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="DefinireFasceOrarie"></a>Setting time bands</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Defining calendars for all notifications
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Scheduled activity management</span> or in <span style="font-weight: bold;">Alarm and event management</span>, define a recurring event calendar (i.e.: fixed holidays) or occasional events (i.e.: mobile holidays). (see chapter <a href="Attivita__fasce_orarie.htm">Activities: time bands</a>).</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <table style="border-left-color: #000000;border-left-width: 1px;border-right-color: #000000;border-right-width: 1px;background-color: #c0c0c0;left: 0px;top: 38px;margin-left: 40px;width: 90%;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" width="90%" bgcolor="#C0C0C0">
                        <col style="width: 6.855%;" />
                        <col style="width: 93.145%;" />
                        <tr valign="top">
                            <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 6.855%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" valign="middle" width="6.855%">
                                <p class="Note">
                                    <img src="../Resources/Images/AAinfo.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />
                                </p>
                            </td>
                            <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 93.145%;padding-right: 1px;padding-left: 1px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" width="93.145%">
                                <p>Calendars are valid for all notification types (alarm or scheduled).</p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="CreareNotificheSchedulate"></a>Creating scheduled activities</p>
        <ol style="list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Creating the action                                                                                                        </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Scheduled activity management</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Actions</span>, create a new action (see chapter <a href="Attivita__azioni.htm">Activities: notification and alarm actions</a>).</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="2">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Defining the action                                                                                                        </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Scheduled activity management</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Actions  </span>open the action details: action pages open (see chapter <a href="Azioni__introduzione.htm">Actions: introduction</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>Open the channel page (i.e.: report) and specify that required (i.e.: select the report) </p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="3">
                            <p>Return to the scheduled activity <span style="font-weight: bold;">Actions</span> page.</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="3">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Setting the action calendar and rules                                                                                                        </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Scheduled activity management</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Time bands</span> indicate the time band when the action can be run (see <a href="Attivita__fasce_orarie.htm">Activity: time band</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Rules</span> select the time band, add it to the required action and enable it (see <a href="Attivita__regole_di_attivazione.htm">Activity: activation rules</a>).</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="3">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Synoptic</span> check the period graph (see <a href="Attivita__sinottico.htm">Activities: synoptic</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="ImpostareNotificheAllarmiEventi"></a>Setting alarm/event notifications and actions</p>
        <ol style="list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Defining single actions
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Alarm and event management</span><span>,  </span><span style="font-weight: bold;">Actions</span><span>,  
 </span>define the single action specifying the recipient (see chapter <a href="Azioni__introduzione.htm">Actions: setup</a>).</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="2">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Defining alarm conditions
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Alarm and event management</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Alarm conditions</span>, select whether the condition is true:</p>
                        </li>
                        <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                            <li class="p" value="1">
                                <p>for any alarm on any device </p>
                            </li>
                            <li class="p" value="2">
                                <p>or for one or more alarms on one or more devices</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>(see chapter <a href="Attivita__condizioni_su_allarme.htm">Notifications: alarm conditions</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                    <p class="ActionDetail">or Defining event conditions</p>
                    <div>
                        <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                            <li class="p" value="1">
                                <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Alarm and event management</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Event conditions</span>, build the logic expression that compares two variables or a variable and a constant</p>
                            </li>
                            <li class="p" value="2">
                                <p>When the logic expression is true, an event is triggered (see chapter  <a href="Attivita__condizioni_su_evento.htm">Notifications: event conditions</a>).</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="3">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Setting the rule that triggers activities                                                                                                        </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Alarm and event managements</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Rules</span>, select an action, a condition, a time band and assign it a rule.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>Enable the rule (see chapter <a href="Attivita__regole_di_attivazione.htm">Notifications: rules</a>).</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="4">
                <p class="ActionDetail">(optional) Disable all alarm and event activities from a device</p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Site configuration</span>, double-click the line, double-click the device, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Main</span><span> page  </span>to disable the alarm and event activities (see chapter <a href="Config-dispositivo__principale.htm">Device setup: main page</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="ActionDetail">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAvedianche.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />See also</p>
        <p><a href="Attivita__concetti_di_base.htm">Activities: basic concepts</a>
        </p>
